node.text: "Don't get mad. Get even." ☝ In honor of #JohnTuckerMustDie's 15th anniversary, take a look back at these throwback interviews with the cast. #TheRewind

node.title: The Rewind: John Tucker Must Die

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by E! News on September 08, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and indoor.

node.text: Jamie Spears has filed to end Britney Spears' conservatorship, and we have exclusive details as to what led Jamie to take the next legal steps. The real reason why is at the link in our bio. (📷: Instagram)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by E! News on September 08, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and people standing.

node.text: Andrew Garfield shared rare insight into his "beautiful" time on The Amazing Spider-Man with his ex, Emma Stone. His favorite memories—and reaction to rumors he'll be reprising his role in Spider-Man: No Way Home—are in our bio. (📷: Getty)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by E! News on September 08, 2021 tagging @rebeccaminkoff. May be an image of 2 people and text that says 'RA THINK THAT THERE'S A LOT TO BE SAID ABOUT GETTING BACK UP AFTER YOU'RE PUNCHED IN THE FACE." -REBECCA MINKOFF #TalesFromTheTop E'.

node.text: Who would have thought that a cut up I ❤️ NY tee could lead to all this? Designer Rebecca Minkoff reveals the best lessons from her road to success, and how getting fired got her there—in our bio. (📷: Getty)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by E! News on September 08, 2021 tagging @elaine4animals. May be an image of 1 person and text that says '@vtbee80 being an adult is so stupid. my friend is coming over and I'm excited to show her my new shower curtain elaine4animals use clear shower curtains cause I'm freak who doesn't want to be taken by surprise if 'm attacked in the shower.'.

node.text: If that happens you gotta R-U-N, get the picture? (📷: @vtbee80/@elaine4animals)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by E! News on September 08, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says '"THERE WAS A CONVERSATION BEFORE THE SERIES STARTED AND I WAS ASRE THE QUESTION, WOULD YOU LIKE RAVEN BAXTER TO BE A LESBIAN?"" -RAVEN-SYMONÉ E'.

node.text: #ThatsSoRaven star Raven-Symoné revealed she was asked prior to the show if she wanted her character to be part of the LGBTQ+ community, similar to her in real life. The reason she said no is in our bio. (📷: Getty)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by E! News on September 08, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, child, people standing and indoor.

node.text: "My daughter has not stayed with me for over 20 months." #TeenMom star Amber Portwood revealed that her relationship with her 12-year-old Leah is still rocky, and claimed her ex Gary and his wife Kristina are "keeping" Leah from her. Link in bio. (📷: Instagram)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by E! News on September 08, 2021 tagging @jordanmcgraw, and @morganstewart. May be an image of 3 people, child, people standing, indoor and text that says 'SAINT'.

node.text: "I can’t hide it anymore.” E!'s very own Morgan Stewart is PREGNANT! 💛 Link in bio for her sweet announcement about baby no. 2. (📷: @morganstewart)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by E! News on September 08, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text: Spotted: Blake Lively making "toddler chic" the style of the season. Forget #NYFW, we're taking notes from this mom at the link in our bio. You know you love her. 💋 (📷: Getty)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by E! News on September 08, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing and indoor.

node.text: Kourtney Kardashian recreated one of Britney Spears' iconic looks circa 2001 and she absolutely worked, b**ch. Link in bio to see. (📷 : Instagram)
